258
00:22:57,572 --> 00:23:00,474
I want you guys to know
how much I appreciate this.

259
00:23:01,316 --> 00:23:03,876
It's been along time
since I've been inside.

260
00:23:03,876 --> 00:23:05,796
-It's our pleasure.
