291
00:26:24,656 --> 00:26:25,736
Thanks.

292
00:26:28,657 --> 00:26:30,064
Wanna have a seat?

293
00:26:46,898 --> 00:26:48,622
Can I ask you something?

294
00:26:48,819 --> 00:26:49,746
Sure.

295
00:26:51,699 --> 00:26:53,586
