331
00:31:20,997 --> 00:31:23,269
I had the misfortune
of being struck down...

332
00:31:23,269 --> 00:31:25,798
...by the most deadly
pair of wild blue eyes...

333
00:31:25,798 --> 00:31:27,813
...God ever had
the audacity to create.

