490
00:44:59,163 --> 00:45:01,138
Happy birthday...

491
00:45:03,324 --> 00:45:04,251
...to you.

492
00:45:07,483 --> 00:45:09,305
Happy birthday...

493
00:45:10,780 --> 00:45:12,668
